#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The exact steps to enable the Linstor Driver depend on your OpenStack "
"distribution. In general, the `python-linstor` package needs to be installed "
"on all hosts running the Cinder volume service. The next section will cover "
"the installation process for common OpenStack distributions."
msgstr ""
"Linstor Driver を有効にする正しい手順は、OpenStack ディストリビューションに"
"よって異なります。一般に `python-linstor` パッケージは、Cinder ボリュームサー"
"ビスを実行しているすべてのホストにインストールする必要があります。次のセク"
"ションでは、一般的な OpenStack ディストリビューションへのインストール手順につ"
"いて説明します。"

#. type: Title =====
#, no-wrap
msgid "DevStack"
msgstr "DevStack"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"https://docs.openstack.org/devstack/latest/[DevStack] is a great way to try "
"out OpenStack in a lab environment.  To use the most recent driver use the "
"following DevStack configuration:"
msgstr ""
"https://docs.openstack.org/devstack/latest/[DevStack] は、ラボ環境で "
"OpenStack を試すのに最適な方法です。最新のドライバーを使用するには、次の "
"DevStack 構成を使用します。"

#. type: Block title
#, no-wrap
msgid "local.conf"
msgstr "local.conf"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# This ensures the Linstor Driver has access to the 'python-linstor' package.\n"
"#\n"
"# This is needed even if using the included driver!\n"
"USE_VENV=True\n"
"ADDITIONAL_VENV_PACKAGES=python-linstor\n"
msgstr ""
"# This ensures the Linstor Driver has access to the 'python-linstor' package.\n"
"#\n"
"# This is needed even if using the included driver!\n"
"USE_VENV=True\n"
"ADDITIONAL_VENV_PACKAGES=python-linstor\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# This is required to select the LINBIT version of the driver\n"
"CINDER_REPO=https://github.com/LINBIT/openstack-cinder.git\n"
"# Replace linstor/stable/victoria with the reference matching your Openstack release.\n"
"CINDER_BRANCH=linstor/stable/victoria\n"
msgstr ""
"# This is required to select the LINBIT version of the driver\n"
"CINDER_REPO=https://github.com/LINBIT/openstack-cinder.git\n"
"# Replace linstor/stable/victoria with the reference matching your Openstack release.\n"
"CINDER_BRANCH=linstor/stable/victoria\n"

#. type: Title =====
#, no-wrap
msgid "Kolla"
msgstr "Kolla"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"https://docs.openstack.org/kolla/latest/[Kolla] packages OpenStack "
"components in containers. They can then be deployed, for example using "
"https://docs.openstack.org/kolla-ansible/latest/[Kolla Ansible] You can take "
"advantage of the available customisation options for kolla containers to set "
"up the Linstor driver."
msgstr ""
"https://docs.openstack.org/kolla/latest/[Kolla] は OpenStack コンポーネントを"
"コンテナーにパッケージ化します。次に、例えば https://docs.openstack.org/"
"kolla-ansible/latest/[Kolla Ansible] を使用してデプロイできます。kolla コンテ"
"ナーで使用可能なカスタマイズオプションを利用して、Linstor ドライバーをセット"
"アップできます。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To ensure that the required `python-linstor` package is installed, use the "
"following override file:"
msgstr ""
"必要な `python-linstor` パッケージがインストールされるようにするには、次の"
"オーバーライドファイルを使用します。"

#. type: Block title
#, no-wrap
msgid "template-override.j2"
msgstr "template-override.j2"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid "{% extends parent_template %}\n"
msgstr "{% extends parent_template %}\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# Cinder\n"
"{% set cinder_base_pip_packages_append = ['python-linstor'] %}\n"
msgstr ""
"# Cinder\n"
"{% set cinder_base_pip_packages_append = ['python-linstor'] %}\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To install the LINBIT version of the driver, update your `kolla-build.conf`"
msgstr ""
"LINBIT バージョンのドライバーをインストールするには `kolla-build.conf` を更新"
"します。"

#. type: Block title
#, no-wrap
msgid "/etc/kolla/kolla-build.conf"
msgstr "/etc/kolla/kolla-build.conf"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[cinder-base]\n"
"type = git\n"
"location = https://github.com/LINBIT/openstack-cinder.git\n"
"# Replace linstor/stable/victoria with the reference matching your Openstack release.\n"
"reference = linstor/stable/victoria\n"
msgstr ""
"[cinder-base]\n"
"type = git\n"
"location = https://github.com/LINBIT/openstack-cinder.git\n"
"# Replace linstor/stable/victoria with the reference matching your Openstack release.\n"
"reference = linstor/stable/victoria\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "To rebuild the Cinder containers, run:"
msgstr "Cinder コンテナを再構築するには、次のコマンドを実行します。"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# A private registry used to store the kolla container images\n"
"REGISTRY=deployment-registry.example.com\n"
"# The image namespace in the registry\n"
"NAMESPACE=kolla\n"
"# The tag to apply to all images. Use the release name for compatibility with kolla-ansible\n"
"TAG=victoria\n"
"kolla-build -t source --template-override template-override.j2 cinder --registry $REGISTRY --namespace $NAMESPACE --tag $TAG\n"
msgstr ""
"# A private registry used to store the kolla container images\n"
"REGISTRY=deployment-registry.example.com\n"
"# The image namespace in the registry\n"
"NAMESPACE=kolla\n"
"# The tag to apply to all images. Use the release name for compatibility with kolla-ansible\n"
"TAG=victoria\n"
"kolla-build -t source --template-override template-override.j2 cinder --registry $REGISTRY --namespace $NAMESPACE --tag $TAG\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "====== Kolla Ansible"
msgstr "====== Kolla Ansible"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"When deploying OpenStack using Kolla Ansible, you need to make sure that:"
msgstr ""
"Kolla Ansible を使用して OpenStack をデプロイする場合は、次のことを確認する必"
"要があります。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "the custom Cinder images, created in the section above, are used"
msgstr "上記のセクションで作成されたカスタム Cinder イメージが使用される"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "deployment of Cinder services is enabled"
msgstr "Cinder サービスのデプロイが有効である"

#. type: Block title
#, no-wrap
msgid "/etc/kolla/globals.yml"
msgstr "/etc/kolla/globals.yml"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# use \"source\" images\n"
"kolla_install_type: source\n"
"# use the same registry as for running kolla-build above\n"
"docker_registry: deployment-registry.example.com\n"
"# use the same namespace as for running kolla-build above\n"
"docker_namespace: kolla\n"
"# deploy cinder block storage service\n"
"enable_cinder: \"yes\"\n"
"# disable verification of cinder backends, kolla-ansible only supports a small subset of available backends for this\n"
"skip_cinder_backend_check: True\n"
"# add the LINSTOR backend to the enabled backends. For backend configuration see below\n"
"cinder_enabled_backends:\n"
"  - name: linstor-drbd\n"
msgstr ""
"# use \"source\" images\n"
"kolla_install_type: source\n"
"# use the same registry as for running kolla-build above\n"
"docker_registry: deployment-registry.example.com\n"
"# use the same namespace as for running kolla-build above\n"
"docker_namespace: kolla\n"
"# deploy cinder block storage service\n"
"enable_cinder: \"yes\"\n"
"# disable verification of cinder backends, kolla-ansible only supports a small subset of available backends for this\n"
"skip_cinder_backend_check: True\n"
"# add the LINSTOR backend to the enabled backends. For backend configuration see below\n"
"cinder_enabled_backends:\n"
"  - name: linstor-drbd\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"You can place the Linstor driver configuration in one of the override "
"directories for kolla-ansible. For more details on the available "
"configuration options, see the section below."
msgstr ""
"Linstor ドライバー構成は kolla-ansible のオーバーライドディレクトリの 1 つに"
"配置できます。使用可能な構成オプションの詳細については、以下のセクションを参"
"照してください。"

#. type: Block title
#, no-wrap
msgid "/etc/kolla/config/cinder/cinder-volume.conf"
msgstr "/etc/kolla/config/cinder/cinder-volume.conf"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[linstor-drbd]\n"
"volume_backend_name = linstor-drbd\n"
"volume_driver = cinder.volume.drivers.linstordrv.LinstorDrbdDriver\n"
"linstor_autoplace_count = 2\n"
"linstor_default_storage_pool_name = cinderpool\n"
"linstor_default_uri = linstor://cinder-01.openstack.test,linstor://cinder-02.openstack.test\n"
msgstr ""
"[linstor-drbd]\n"
"volume_backend_name = linstor-drbd\n"
"volume_driver = cinder.volume.drivers.linstordrv.LinstorDrbdDriver\n"
"linstor_autoplace_count = 2\n"
"linstor_default_storage_pool_name = cinderpool\n"
"linstor_default_uri = linstor://cinder-01.openstack.test,linstor://cinder-02.openstack.test\n"

#. type: Title =====
#, no-wrap
msgid "OpenStack Ansible"
msgstr "OpenStack Ansible"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"https://docs.openstack.org/openstack-ansible/[OpenStack Ansible] provides "
"Ansible playbooks to configure and deploy of OpenStack environments. It "
"allows for fine-grained customization of the deployment, letting you set up "
"the Linstor driver directly."
msgstr ""
"https://docs.openstack.org/openstack-ansible/[OpenStack Ansible] は、"
"OpenStack 環境を構成およびデプロイするための Ansible プレイブックを提供しま"
"す。これにより、デプロイメントをきめ細かくカスタマイズできるため、Linstor ド"
"ライバーを直接セットアップできます。"

#. type: Block title
#, no-wrap
msgid "/etc/openstack_ansile/user_variables.yml"
msgstr "/etc/openstack_ansile/user_variables.yml"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"cinder_git_repo: https://github.com/LINBIT/openstack-cinder.git\n"
"cinder_git_install_branch: linstor/stable/victoria\n"
msgstr ""
"cinder_git_repo: https://github.com/LINBIT/openstack-cinder.git\n"
"cinder_git_install_branch: linstor/stable/victoria\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"cinder_user_pip_packages:\n"
"  - python-linstor\n"
msgstr ""
"cinder_user_pip_packages:\n"
"  - python-linstor\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"cinder_backends: <1>\n"
"  linstor-drbd:\n"
"   volume_backend_name: linstor-drbd\n"
"   volume_driver: cinder.volume.drivers.linstordrv.LinstorDrbdDriver\n"
"   linstor_autoplace_count: 2\n"
"   linstor_default_storage_pool_name: cinderpool\n"
"   linstor_default_uri: linstor://cinder-01.openstack.test,linstor://cinder-02.openstack.test\n"
msgstr ""
"cinder_backends: <1>\n"
"  linstor-drbd:\n"
"   volume_backend_name: linstor-drbd\n"
"   volume_driver: cinder.volume.drivers.linstordrv.LinstorDrbdDriver\n"
"   linstor_autoplace_count: 2\n"
"   linstor_default_storage_pool_name: cinderpool\n"
"   linstor_default_uri: linstor://cinder-01.openstack.test,linstor://cinder-02.openstack.test\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"A detailed description of the available backend parameters can be found in "
"the section below"
msgstr ""
"使用可能なバックエンドパラメータの詳細な説明は、以下のセクションにあります。"

#. type: Title =====
#, no-wrap
msgid "Generic Cinder deployment"
msgstr "汎用 Cinder デプロイメント"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"For other forms of OpenStack deployments, this guide can only provide non-"
"specific hints."
msgstr ""
"他の形式の OpenStack デプロイメントの場合、このガイドでは一般的なヒントのみを"
"提供できます。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To update the Linstor driver version, find your cinder installation. Some "
"likely paths are:"
msgstr ""
"Linstor ドライバーのバージョンを更新するには、インストールされた cinder ディ"
"レクトリを見つけてください。考えられるパスは次のとおりです。"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"/usr/lib/python3.6/dist-packages/cinder/\n"
"/usr/lib/python3.6/site-packages/cinder/\n"
"/usr/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/cinder/\n"
"/usr/lib/python2.7/site-packages/cinder/\n"
msgstr ""
"/usr/lib/python3.6/dist-packages/cinder/\n"
"/usr/lib/python3.6/site-packages/cinder/\n"
"/usr/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/cinder/\n"
"/usr/lib/python2.7/site-packages/cinder/\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The Linstor driver consists of a single file called `linstordrv.py`, located "
"in the Cinder directory:"
msgstr ""
"Linstor ドライバーは、cinder ディレクトリにある `linstordrv.py` というファイ"
"ルです。"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid "$CINDER_PATH/volume/drivers/linstordrv.py\n"
msgstr "$CINDER_PATH/volume/drivers/linstordrv.py\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To update the driver, replace the file with one from the LINBIT repository"
msgstr ""
"ドライバを更新するには、ファイルを LINBIT リポジトリのファイルに置き換えます"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"RELEASE=linstor/stable/victoria\n"
"curl -fL \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LINBIT/openstack-cinder/$RELEASE/cinder/volume/drivers/linstordrv.py\" > $CINDER_PATH/volume/drivers/linstordrv.py\n"
msgstr ""
"RELEASE=linstor/stable/victoria\n"
"curl -fL \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LINBIT/openstack-cinder/$RELEASE/cinder/volume/drivers/linstordrv.py\" > $CINDER_PATH/volume/drivers/linstordrv.py\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"You might also need to remove the Python cache for the update to be "
"registered:"
msgstr ""
"登録されたものを更新するには、Python キャッシュを削除する必要がある場合もあり"
"ます。"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid "rm -rf $CINDER_PATH/volume/drivers/__pycache__\n"
msgstr "rm -rf $CINDER_PATH/volume/drivers/__pycache__\n"

#. type: Title ===
#, no-wrap
msgid "Configure a Linstor Backend for Cinder"
msgstr "Cinder 用の Linstor バックエンドを構成"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To use the Linstor driver, configure the Cinder volume service. This is done "
"by editing the Cinder configuration file and then restarting the Cinder "
"Volume service."
msgstr ""
"Linstor ドライバーを使用するには、Cinder ボリュームサービスを構成します。"
"Cinder 構成ファイルを編集してから、Cinder ボリュームサービスを再起動すること"
"で構成できます。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Most of the time, the Cinder configuration file is located at `/etc/cinder/"
"cinder.conf`. Some deployment options allow manipulating this file in "
"advance. See the section above for specifics."
msgstr ""
"ほとんどの場合、Cinder 構成ファイルは `/etc/cinder/cinder.conf` にあります。"
"一部のデプロイメントでは、このファイルを事前に編集できます。詳細は上記のセク"
"ションを参照してください。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To configure a new volume backend using Linstor, add the following section "
"to `cinder.conf`"
msgstr ""
"Linstor を使用して新しいボリュームバックエンドを構成するには、次のセクション"
"を `cinder.conf` に追加します。"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[linstor-drbd]\n"
"volume_backend_name = linstor-drbd <1>\n"
"volume_driver = cinder.volume.drivers.linstordrv.LinstorDrbdDriver <2>\n"
"linstor_default_uri = linstor://cinder-01.openstack.test,linstor://cinder-02.openstack.test <3>\n"
"linstor_default_storage_pool_name = cinderpool <4>\n"
"linstor_autoplace_count = 2 <5>\n"
"linstor_controller_diskless = true <6>\n"
"... <7>\n"
msgstr ""
"[linstor-drbd]\n"
"volume_backend_name = linstor-drbd <1>\n"
"volume_driver = cinder.volume.drivers.linstordrv.LinstorDrbdDriver <2>\n"
"linstor_default_uri = linstor://cinder-01.openstack.test,linstor://cinder-02.openstack.test <3>\n"
"linstor_default_storage_pool_name = cinderpool <4>\n"
"linstor_autoplace_count = 2 <5>\n"
"linstor_controller_diskless = true <6>\n"
"... <7>\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The parameters described here are based on the latest release provided by "
"Linbit. The driver included in OpenStack might not support all of these "
"parameters. Take a look at the https://docs.openstack.org/cinder/latest/"
"configuration/block-storage/drivers/linstor-driver.html[OpenStack driver "
"documentation] to find out more."
msgstr ""
"ここで説明するパラメーターは、Linbit が提供する最新のリリースに基づいていま"
"す。 OpenStack に含まれているドライバーは、これらのパラメーターのすべてをサ"
"ポートしているとは限りません。詳細は https://docs.openstack.org/cinder/"
"latest/configuration/block-storage/drivers/linstor-driver.html[OpenStack ドラ"
"イバーのドキュメント] を参照ください。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The name of the volume backend. Needs to be unique in the Cinder "
"configuration. The whole section should share the same name. This name is "
"referenced again in `cinder.conf` in the `enabled_backends` setting and when "
"creating a new volume type."
msgstr ""
"ボリュームバックエンド名。 Cinder 構成で一意である必要があります。セクション"
"全体で同じ名前を共有する必要があります。この名前は `enabled_backends` 設定の "
"`cinder.conf` で、および新しいボリュームタイプを作成するときに再び参照されま"
"す。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "The version of the Linstor driver to use. There are two options:"
msgstr "使用する Linstor ドライバーのバージョン。2 つのオプションがあります。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "`cinder.volume.drivers.linstordrv.LinstorDrbdDriver`"
msgstr "`cinder.volume.drivers.linstordrv.LinstorDrbdDriver`"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "`cinder.volume.drivers.linstordrv.LinstorIscsiDriver`"
msgstr "`cinder.volume.drivers.linstordrv.LinstorIscsiDriver`"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Which driver you should use depends on your Linstor set up and requirements. "
"Details on each choice are documented in <<s-openstack-linstor-transport-"
"options, the section below.>>"
msgstr ""
"どのドライバーを使用するかは Linstor のセットアップと要件によって異なります。"
"各選択肢の詳細は <<s-openstack-linstor-transport-options, 以下のセクション>> "
"を参照ください。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The URL(s) of the Linstor Controller(s). Multiple Controllers can be "
"specified to make use of <<s-linstor_ha,Linstor High Availability>>. If not "
"set, defaults to `linstor://localhost`."
msgstr ""
"Linstor コントローラーの URL。 <<s-linstor_ha,Linstor 高可用性>> を利用するた"
"めに、複数のコントローラーを指定できます。設定されていない場合、デフォルトは "
"`linstor://localhost` です。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The storage pools to use when placing resources. Applies to all diskfull "
"resources created. Defaults to `DfltStorPool`."
msgstr ""
"リソースを配置するときに使用するストレージプール。作成されたすべてのディスク"
"フルリソースに適用されます。デフォルトは `DfltStorPool` です。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The number of replicas to create for the given volume. A value of `0` will "
"create a replica on all nodes. Defaults to `0`."
msgstr ""
"特定のボリュームに対して作成する複製数。値が `0` の場合、すべてのノードに複製"
"が作成されます。デフォルトは `0` です。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"If set to true, ensures that at least one (diskless) replica is deployed on "
"the Cinder Controller host. This is useful for ISCSI transports. Defaults to "
"`true`."
msgstr ""
"true に設定すると、少なくとも 1 つの（ディスクレス）複製が Cinder コントロー"
"ラーホストにデプロイされることを保証します。これは、iSCSIトランスポートに役立"
"ちます。デフォルトは `true`です。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"You can specify more generic Cinder options here, for example `target_helper "
"= tgtadm` for the ISCSI connector."
msgstr ""
"ここでは、より一般的な Cinder オプションを指定できます。たとえば、iSCSI コネ"
"クタの場合は `target_helper = tgtadm` です。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"You can also configure multiple Linstor backends, choosing a different name "
"and configuration options for each."
msgstr ""
"複数の Linstor バックエンドを構成して、それぞれに異なる名前と構成オプションを"
"選択することもできます。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"After configuring the Linstor backend, it should also be enabled. Add it to "
"the list of enabled backends in `cinder.conf`, and optionally set is as the "
"default backend:"
msgstr ""
"Linstor バックエンドを構成した後、それも有効にする必要があります。これを "
"`cinder.conf` の有効なバックエンドのリストに追加し、オプションでデフォルトの"
"バックエンドとして設定します。"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[DEFAULT]\n"
"...\n"
"default_volume_type = linstor-drbd-volume\n"
"enabled_backends = lvm,linstor-drbd\n"
"...\n"
msgstr ""
"[DEFAULT]\n"
"...\n"
"default_volume_type = linstor-drbd-volume\n"
"enabled_backends = lvm,linstor-drbd\n"
"...\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"As a last step, if you changed the Cinder configuration or updated the "
"driver itself, make sure to restart the Cinder service(s). Please check the "
"documentation for your OpenStack Distribution on how to restart services."
msgstr ""
"最後のステップとして、Cinder 構成を変更した場合、またはドライバー自体を更新し"
"た場合は、必ず Cinder サービスを再起動してください。サービスを再起動する方法"
"については、OpenStack ディストリビューションのドキュメントを確認してくださ"
"い。"

#. type: Title ====
#, no-wrap
msgid "Choice of Transport Protocol"
msgstr "トランスポートプロトコルの選択"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The Transport Protocol in Cinder is how clients (for example nova-compute) "
"access the actual volumes. With Linstor, you can choose between two "
"different drivers that use different transports."
msgstr ""
"Cinder のトランスポートプロトコルは、クライアント（たとえば、nova-compute）が"
"実際のボリュームにアクセスする方法です。Linstor を使用すると、異なるトランス"
"ポートを使用する 2 つの異なるドライバーを選択できます。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"`cinder.volume.drivers.linstordrv.LinstorDrbdDriver`, which uses DRBD as "
"transport"
msgstr ""
"`cinder.volume.drivers.linstordrv.LinstorDrbdDriver` : トランスポートプロトコ"
"ルとして DRBD を使用"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"`cinder.volume.drivers.linstordrv.LinstorIscsiDriver`, which uses ISCSI as "
"transport"
msgstr ""
"`cinder.volume.drivers.linstordrv.LinstorIscsiDriver` : トランスポートプロト"
"コルとして iSCSI を使用"

#. type: Title =====
#, no-wrap
msgid "Using DRBD as Transport Protocol"
msgstr "トランスポートプロトコルとして DRBD を使用"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The `LinstorDrbdDriver` works by ensuring a replica of the volume is "
"available locally on the node where a client (i.e. nova-compute) issued a "
"request. This only works if _all_ compute nodes are also running Linstor "
"Satellites that are part of the same Linstor cluster."
msgstr ""
"`LinstorDrbdDriver` は、クライアント（つまり、nova-compute）がリクエストを発"
"行したノードでボリュームの複製がローカルで利用できるようにすることで機能しま"
"す。これはすべての compute ノードが同じ Linstor クラスターの一部である "
"Linstor サテライトを実行している場合にのみ機能します。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "The advantages of this option are:"
msgstr "このオプションの利点は次のとおりです。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Once set up, the Cinder host is no longer involved in the data path. All "
"read and write to the volume are handled by the local DRBD module, which "
"will handle replication across its configured peers."
msgstr ""
"セットアップが完了すると、Cinder ホストはデータパスに関与しなくなります。ボ"
"リュームへのすべての読み書きは、構成された対向ノード間でのレプリケーションを"
"処理するローカル DRBD モジュールによって処理されます。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Since the Cinder host is not involved in the data path, any disruptions to "
"the Cinder service do not affect volumes that are already attached."
msgstr ""
"Cinder ホストはデータパスに関与していないため、Cinder サービスが中断しても、"
"すでに接続されているボリュームには影響しません。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"A drawback is the reduced compatibility: Not all hosts and hypervisors "
"support using DRBD volumes. This restricts deployment to Linux hosts and "
"`kvm` hypervisors."
msgstr ""
"欠点は、互換性が低下することです。すべてのホストとハイパーバイザーが DRBD ボ"
"リュームの使用をサポートしているわけではありません。これにより、Linux ホスト"
"と `kvm` ハイパーバイザーがデプロイメント対象と制限されます。"

#. type: Title =====
#, no-wrap
msgid "Using ISCSI as Transport Protocol"
msgstr "iSCSI トランスポートプロトコルを使用"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The default way to export Cinder volumes is via iSCSI. This brings the "
"advantage of maximum compatibility - iSCSI can be used with every "
"hypervisor, be it VMWare, Xen, HyperV, or KVM."
msgstr ""
"Cinder ボリュームをエクスポートするデフォルトの方法は、iSCSI 経由です。これに"
"より最大の互換性が得られます。iSCSI は、VMWare、Xen、HyperV、または KVM など"
"のあらゆるハイパーバイザーで使用できます。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The drawback is that all data has to be sent to a Cinder node, to be "
"processed by an (userspace) iSCSI daemon; that means that the data needs to "
"pass the kernel/userspace border, and these transitions will cost some "
"performance."
msgstr ""
"欠点は、すべてのデータを（ユーザースペースの）iSCSI デーモンで処理するために"
"Cinder ノードに送信する必要があることです。これは、データがカーネル/ユーザス"
"ペース境界を通過する必要があることを意味し、パフォーマンスに影響を与えます。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Another drawback is the introduction of a single point of failure. If a "
"Cinder node running the iSCSI daemon crashes, other nodes lose access to "
"their volumes.  There are ways to configure Cinder for automatic fail-over "
"to mitigate this, but it requires considerable effort."
msgstr ""
"もう1つの欠点は、単一障害点になりうる点です。iSCSI デーモンを実行している "
"Cinder ノードがクラッシュすると、他のノードはボリュームにアクセスできなくなり"
"ます。これを軽減するために自動フェイルオーバー用に Cinder を構成する方法はい"
"くつかありますが、かなりの労力が必要です。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"For ISCSI to work, the Cinder host needs access to a local replica of every "
"volume. This can be achieved by either setting "
"`linstor_controller_diskless=True` or using `linstor_autoplace_count=0`."
msgstr ""
"iSCSI が機能するには、Cinder ホストがすべてのボリュームのローカルレプリカにア"
"クセスする必要があります。これは `linstor_controller_diskless=True` を設定す"
"るか、 `linstor_autoplace_count=0` を使用することで実現できます。"

#. type: Title ====
#, no-wrap
msgid "Verify status of Linstor backends"
msgstr "Linstor バックエンドのステータスを確認"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To verify that all backends are up and running, you can use the OpenStack "
"command line client:"
msgstr ""
"すべてのバックエンドが稼働していることを確認するには、OpenStack コマンドライ"
"ンを使用できます。"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ openstack volume service list\n"
"+------------------+----------------------------------------+------+---------+-------+----------------------------+\n"
"| Binary           | Host                                   | Zone | Status  | State | Updated At                 |\n"
"+------------------+----------------------------------------+------+---------+-------+----------------------------+\n"
"| cinder-scheduler | cinder-01.openstack.test               | nova | enabled | up    | 2021-03-10T12:24:37.000000 |\n"
"| cinder-volume    | cinder-01.openstack.test@linstor-drbd  | nova | enabled | up    | 2021-03-10T12:24:34.000000 |\n"
"| cinder-volume    | cinder-01.openstack.test@linstor-iscsi | nova | enabled | up    | 2021-03-10T12:24:35.000000 |\n"
"+------------------+----------------------------------------+------+---------+-------+----------------------------+\n"
msgstr ""
"$ openstack volume service list\n"
"+------------------+----------------------------------------+------+---------+-------+----------------------------+\n"
"| Binary           | Host                                   | Zone | Status  | State | Updated At                 |\n"
"+------------------+----------------------------------------+------+---------+-------+----------------------------+\n"
"| cinder-scheduler | cinder-01.openstack.test               | nova | enabled | up    | 2021-03-10T12:24:37.000000 |\n"
"| cinder-volume    | cinder-01.openstack.test@linstor-drbd  | nova | enabled | up    | 2021-03-10T12:24:34.000000 |\n"
"| cinder-volume    | cinder-01.openstack.test@linstor-iscsi | nova | enabled | up    | 2021-03-10T12:24:35.000000 |\n"
"+------------------+----------------------------------------+------+---------+-------+----------------------------+\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"If you have the Horizon GUI deployed, check `Admin > System Information > "
"Block Storage Service` instead."
msgstr ""
"Horizon GUI をデプロイしている場合は、代わりに `Admin > System Information > "
"Block Storage Service` を確認してください。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"In the above example all configured services are `enabled` and `up`. If "
"there are any issues, please check the logs of the Cinder Volume service."
msgstr ""
"上記の例では、構成されているすべてのサービスが `enabled` と `up` になっていま"
"す。問題がある場合は、Cinder ボリュームサービスのログを確認してください。"

#. type: Title ===
#, no-wrap
msgid "Create a new volume type for Linstor"
msgstr "Linstor の新しいボリュームタイプを作成"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Before creating volumes using Cinder, you have to create a volume type. This "
"can either be done via the command line:"
msgstr ""
"Cinder を使用してボリュームを作成する前に、ボリュームタイプを作成する必要があ"
"ります。これは、コマンドラインから実行できます。"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# Create a volume using the default backend\n"
"$ openstack volume type create default\n"
"+-------------+--------------------------------------+\n"
"| Field       | Value                                |\n"
"+-------------+--------------------------------------+\n"
"| description | None                                 |\n"
"| id          | 58365ffb-959a-4d91-8821-5d72e5c39c26 |\n"
"| is_public   | True                                 |\n"
"| name        | default                              |\n"
"+-------------+--------------------------------------+\n"
"# Create a volume using a specific backend\n"
"$ openstack volume type create --property volume_backend_name=linstor-drbd linstor-drbd-volume\n"
"+-------------+--------------------------------------+\n"
"| Field       | Value                                |\n"
